    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the requirements for using multiple Generic Associated Channel Labels (GALs) in an MPLS label stack. As a result, the document updates RFC 5586 by removing the restriction imposed on the usage of GAL that limits the number of GAL in the MPLS label stack to one.</t>
